 Implement the blockchain nodes that will form the network and communicate with each other. Each node will maintain a copy of the blockchain and will be responsible for validating transactions and adding new blocks. 

Develop the smart contracts: Develop the smart contracts that will be deployed on the blockchain. Smart contracts are self-executing programs that can automate the execution of complex business logic and enforce the rules of the blockchain.

Test and deploy the blockchain: Test the blockchain thoroughly to ensure that it functions as intended and is secure against attacks. Deploy the blockchain on a public or private network, depending on the use case. Build Blockchain Project

Maintain and upgrade the blockchain: Maintain and upgrade the blockchain as needed to fix bugs, add new features, and improve performance. 
